Risk Assessment Table
--------------------------------------------------

Vulnerability	Likelihood	Impact	Risk Score	Risk Level
vsftpd 2.3.4 Backdoor	High (3)	High (3)	9	Critical
Telnet Service Enabled	High (3)	High (3)	9	Critical
